							<div class="post_header">
								<div id="crumbs"><a href="http://www.extraenvironmentalist.com">Home</a> &raquo; <a href="http://www.extraenvironmentalist.com/category/podcast/" title="View all posts in Podcast Episodes">Podcast Episodes</a> &raquo; <span class="current">[ Episode #62 // Land Grabs ]</span></div><br/>
								<h3 class="cufon single black">
									[ Episode #62 // Land Grabs ]								</h3>
								<div class="post_detail">
									Posted by:&nbsp;Justin&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
									Tags:&nbsp;
									<a href="http://www.extraenvironmentalist.com/tag/africa/" rel="tag">africa</a>, <a href="http://www.extraenvironmentalist.com/tag/agriculture/" rel="tag">agriculture</a>, <a href="http://www.extraenvironmentalist.com/tag/china/" rel="tag">china</a>, <a href="http://www.extraenvironmentalist.com/tag/collapse/" rel="tag">collapse</a>, <a href="http://www.extraenvironmentalist.com/tag/complexity/" rel="tag">complexity</a>, <a href="http://www.extraenvironmentalist.com/tag/ecology/" rel="tag">ecology</a>, <a href="http://www.extraenvironmentalist.com/tag/economics/" rel="tag">economics</a>, <a href="http://www.extraenvironmentalist.com/tag/energy/" rel="tag">energy</a>, <a href="http://www.extraenvironmentalist.com/tag/expectations/" rel="tag">expectations</a>, <a href="http://www.extraenvironmentalist.com/tag/farming/" rel="tag">farming</a>, <a href="http://www.extraenvironmentalist.com/tag/finance/" rel="tag">finance</a>, <a href="http://www.extraenvironmentalist.com/tag/financialization/" rel="tag">financialization</a>, <a href="http://www.extraenvironmentalist.com/tag/growth/" rel="tag">growth</a>, <a href="http://www.extraenvironmentalist.com/tag/money/" rel="tag">money</a>, <a href="http://www.extraenvironmentalist.com/tag/oecd/" rel="tag">OECD</a>, <a href="http://www.extraenvironmentalist.com/tag/peak-oil/" rel="tag">peak oil</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
									Posted date:&nbsp;
									June 30, 2013 									&nbsp;|&nbsp;
									<span class="dsq-postid" rel="2886 http://www.extraenvironmentalist.com/?p=2886">2 Comments</span>								</div>
